		"description": "Comprehensive Postman collection for testing the CV Processing Application endpoints. This collection includes all API endpoints for file upload, CV processing, field extraction, validation, and monitoring.\n\n## Features:\n- Complete API endpoint coverage\n- Automated test scenarios with CV samples\n- Error handling and edge case testing\n- Automatic requestId management\n- Health checks and monitoring\n\n## Usage:\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set the baseUrl variable (default: http://localhost:8080)\n3. Run the test scenarios to validate the complete workflow\n4. Use the CV-1.md and CV-2.md files for file upload tests",
